    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Several users have requested the ability to set decorators and filters for form elements en masse:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
$form-&gt;addGlobalDecorator('HtmlTag', array('tag' =&gt; 'div', 'class' =&gt; 'foobar'));

$form-&gt;addGlobalFilter('StringTrim');
</code></pre>

<p>This would simplify setup of the form elements and keep things DRY.</p>

